def load_top_genes_from_file(filename):
    '''
    Load list of gene names from top saved file
    '''
    with open(filename, 'r') as f:
        genes = [x.strip() for x in f.readlines()]
    
    return genes

def view_df(df):
    '''Small function to display df gene info '''
    print(f"Gene count: {len(df['locus_tag'].unique())}")
    #return df[['mage_id','mage_gene','locus_tag','gene_symbol','product','regulation','notes']].drop_duplicates().sort_values('locus_tag').reset_index()
    return df[['mage_id','mage_gene','locus_tag','gene_symbol','product']].drop_duplicates().sort_values('locus_tag').reset_index()

def altair_pcoords_plot_mark_goi(df,title,xorder='exp_condition_order'):
    # If more than 30 entries, make 2 columns
    col_num = 1 if len(df['locus_tag'].unique()) <=50 else 2
    
    highlight = alt.selection(type='single', on='mouseover',
                              fields=['desc_string'], nearest=True)
    
    selection = alt.selection_multi(fields=['desc_string'], bind='legend')


    base = alt.Chart(df.sort_values(xorder),
                     title=title
        ).encode(
        x=alt.X(f'{xorder}:N',
                sort=alt.EncodingSortField(field=f"{xorder}:N", op="count")
               ),
        y='mean:Q',
        #color='locus_tag:N',
        detail='desc_string:N',
        
        shape=alt.Shape('desc_string:N',
                        legend=alt.Legend(title='Gene', 
                                          orient = 'right',
                                          labelLimit=0,
                                          columns=col_num,
                                          symbolLimit=200
                                         )),
        color=alt.Color('marked:N', scale=None),
        size=alt.value(100)
        #opacity=alt.condition(highlight, alt.value(1), alt.value(0.2)),
        
    )
    

    lines = base.mark_line().encode(
        size=alt.condition((selection|highlight), alt.value(5), alt.value(2)),
        opacity=alt.condition((selection|highlight), alt.value(1), alt.value(0.5))
    ).add_selection(
        selection,
    ).properties(
         width=600,
         height=400
    ).interactive()
    
    
    points = base.mark_circle().encode(
        tooltip=['locus_tag','product','type','gene_symbol','mage_gene','desc_string:N'],
        #tooltip=['locus_tag','product','type','gene_symbol','mage_gene','desc_string:N'],
        opacity=alt.condition((selection|highlight), alt.value(1), alt.value(0.2)),
        size=alt.condition((selection|highlight), alt.value(100), alt.value(3))
    ).add_selection(highlight)

    #return points + lines
    return lines + points



def altair_pcoords_plot_select_legend_and_highlight(df,title,xorder='exp_condition_order'):
    # If more than 30 entries, make 2 columns
    col_num = 1 if len(df['locus_tag'].unique()) <=50 else 2
    
    highlight = alt.selection(type='single', on='mouseover',
                              fields=['desc_string'], nearest=True)
    
    selection = alt.selection_multi(fields=['desc_string'], bind='legend')


    base = alt.Chart(df.sort_values(xorder),
                     title=title
        ).encode(
        x=alt.X(f'{xorder}:N',
                sort=alt.EncodingSortField(field=f"{xorder}:N", op="count")
               ),
        y='mean:Q',
        #color='locus_tag:N',
        color=alt.Color('desc_string:N',
                        legend=alt.Legend(title='Gene', 
                                          orient = 'right',
                                          labelLimit=0,
                                          columns=col_num,
                                          symbolLimit=200
                                         )),
        size=alt.value(100)
        #opacity=alt.condition(highlight, alt.value(1), alt.value(0.2)),
        
    )
    

    lines = base.mark_line().encode(
        size=alt.condition((selection|highlight), alt.value(3), alt.value(1)),
        opacity=alt.condition((selection|highlight), alt.value(1), alt.value(0.5))
    ).add_selection(
        selection,
    ).properties(
         width=600,
         height=400
    ).interactive()
    
    
    points = base.mark_circle().encode(
        #tooltip=['locus_tag','product','type','gene_symbol','mage_gene','desc_string:N','notes'],
        tooltip=['locus_tag','product','type','gene_symbol','mage_gene','desc_string:N'],
        opacity=alt.condition((selection|highlight), alt.value(1), alt.value(0.2)),
        size=alt.condition((selection|highlight), alt.value(100), alt.value(3))
    ).add_selection(highlight)

    #return points + lines
    return lines + points
